{"type": "article", "id": 16908, "title": "漂浮的灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-02T06:50:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105822fkVy2LWM7dwQvmhz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏漂浮的灯来自一个设计二人组 Spitsberg，成立于荷兰阿姆斯特丹。他们在灯的正下方用钢丝吊住了一个用半透明尼龙布做的圆盘，当灯光照射在上面，就改变了光的颜色，也有一种朦胧美，适合悬挂在家中，很轻盈。下面的圆盘可选红色、黑色和裸色，搭配黑色或灰色的骨架。售价 650 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.spitsberg.nl/products/floating-light\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144143siyg9SeOvWw3GRz8.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"325\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68855932\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144144E19AfP0XbgwNVBqk.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"662\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68958333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144145X90uLcxJR7VUGjwH.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144145rBFxLqVQuTHzsEbh.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"1308\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.3625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}